					<TBODY>
						<TR>
						<TD width=70>&nbsp;</TD>
						<TD width=530><font size='4' color=#010080><b>건설업 경쟁력강화 방안(전문) </b></font></TD></TR>
					</TBODY>
				</TABLE>	
				<TABLE border=0 cellPadding=2 cellSpacing=1 width=600>
					<TBODY>
						<TR>
						<TD width=550 align=right class=view><font color=#010080>
		<a href='mailto:leeki@moneytoday.co.kr'>이기형</a>기자 	&nbsp; | &nbsp; 08/30 07:48 &nbsp; | &nbsp; 조회 228 &nbsp; &nbsp;</font></TD></TR> 		
